{"word":"ἐπιπίπτω","slug":"ἐπιπίπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιπίπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πεσοῦμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to fall upon</i> or <i>over</i> another, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to fall upon, attack, assail</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; of storms, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: of disease and accidents, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}